description:
Focus on learning what you need to pass the CFA Level I exam. Studying what will not be tested is wasted time - time you cannot afford to lose.

Study efficiently with 41 hours of straightforward, visual, and engaging video lessons by Mike Carmody, CFA, FSA, MAAA, which average 10 minutes and correspond to CFA Institute readings. Master complex math and financial problems by following our visual solving steps. Grasp complex financial and economic concepts through simple visuals and explanations. Walk into the exam with Confidence.
